---
title: Harissa Chickpea Stew with Spiced Flatbread Crisps and Feta
description: Protein-packed chickpeas get a North African-style treatment in this hearty and fragrant stew. You'll love dunking the spiced flatbread crisps into this veggie-filled wonder!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-pois-chiches-au-harissa-f91f0975.jpg
